[At her news conference for Japanese reporters, one economics
journalist summed up the Japanese sense of relief.]65 ["My impression
was that you would be a scary old lady,"]66 [he said,]67 [drawing a
few nervous chuckles from his colleagues.]68 ["But I am relieved to
see]69 [that you are beautiful and gentle and intelligent and a person
